OL,3,CArmed police deployed to Kendal after
OL,4,Cman stabbed
OL,6,FResidents in Kendal have been told
OL,7,Fthey may see 'a larger-than-usual'
OL,8,Fpolice presence in the area after a
OL,9,Fman was stabbed.
OL,11,FCumbria Police say officers responded
OL,12,Fto the incident on Aspen Close just
OL,13,Fafter 9:30 on Friday morning (3 April).
OL,15,FA man, in his 20s, sustained a stab
OL,16,Fwound to his hand.
