OL,3,CArmed police deployed to Kendal after
OL,4,Cman stabbed
OL,6,FHis injuries are not thought to be
OL,7,Fserious or life-threatening and
OL,8,Fofficers want to reassure people that
OL,9,Fthere is no perceived threat to the
OL,10,Fwider public at this time.
OL,12,FCumbria Police have said: "Enquiries
OL,13,Fare currently being carried out and
OL,14,Fresidents in the area may see a larger-
OL,15,Fthan-usual police presence as searches
OL,16,Fare executed.
