OL,3,CArmed police deployed to Kendal after
OL,4,Cman stabbed
OL,6,F"Armed police have also been deployed
OL,7,Fas a precaution due to the nature of
OL,8,Fthe assault. We would like to reassure
OL,9,Fpeople there is no perceived threat to
OL,10,Fthe public at this time.
OL,12,F"Anyone with any information relating
OL,13,Fto the incident is asked to contact
OL,14,Fpolice on 999."
